title: Led Zeppelin - 1980.06.23 Bremen, Gemany (Remaster)
description:
Led Zeppelin - 1980.06.23 Bremen, Gemany    

Led Zeppelin
Stadthalle, Bremen, Germany
June 23th, 1980
SBD-Main AUD-Patching
Winston Remasters

SBD Source - 1stGenCassette>DAT2>Remaster
AUD Source - 1stGenCassette>DAT2>2CDR3>Remaster

Live Omega Series #5

Winstons Disclaimer: Remastering is just a Hobby.. 
take it and enjoy or just pass on it. The choice is 
yours. This version is never meant to be definitive.

Almost Complete show. Missing 10-15 seconds Stairway 
to Heaven where SBD Ends AUD Begins.

Sources Digitally Enhanced with Samplitude. 

Tracklist:

LZ 1980-06-23 D1T01 - Train Kept a Rollin
LZ 1980-06-23 D1T02 - Nobodys Fault but Mine
LZ 1980-06-23 D1T03 - Black Dog
LZ 1980-06-23 D1T04 - In The Evening
LZ 1980-06-23 D1T05 - Rain Song
LZ 1980-06-23 D1T06 - Hot Dog
LZ 1980-06-23 D1T07 - All of My Love
LZ 1980-06-23 D1T08 - Trampled Underfoot
LZ 1980-06-23 D1T09 - Since Ive Been Loving You
LZ 1980-06-23 D1T10 - Achilles Last Stand
LZ 1980-06-23 D2T01 - White Summer
LZ 1980-06-23 D2T02 - Black Mountainside
LZ 1980-06-23 D2T03 - Kashmir
LZ 1980-06-23 D2T04 - Stairway To Heaven
LZ 1980-06-23 D2T05 - Rock and Roll
LZ 1980-06-23 D2T06 - Communication Breakdown

Comments: 
Not a bad show but no tops tonight. Jimmy as alaways is missing 
some notes here and there but overall a very good show. Nice 
versions of Trampled Underfoot, Achilles Last Stand and Kashmir. 
A short and compact Communication Breakdown closing this rather 
low-key gig
